---
/**
 * PromiseSection.astro – The promise statement for JP Tadduni Transmissions.
 * Red accent section positioned between Pain Chain and Services grid.
 */
---

<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-20 overflow-hidden bg-jp-black">

  <!-- Red glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(204,0,0,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Top/bottom red glow lines -->
  <div class="section-divider absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
  <div class="section-divider absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center relative z-10">

    <!-- Label -->
    <p class="font-body text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-jp-red mb-6">The JP Tadduni Promise</p>

    <!-- Promise statement -->
    <blockquote class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl text-jp-white leading-snug">
      One call to JP Tadduni and we diagnose the real problem, give you a straight quote,
      and rebuild it right —&nbsp;
      <span class="text-jp-red">so it lasts another 100,000 miles.</span>
    </blockquote>

    <!-- Supporting details -->
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-jp-muted">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-jp-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        Honest Diagnosis First
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-jp-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        No Surprise Charges
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-jp-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        Written Warranty Included
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-jp-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        Ready in 3–5 Business Days
      </span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
